Package FLOTF

Class Part

  • java.lang.Object
    • FLOTF.Part
  • public class Part
extends java.lang.Object
    This class creates an NSN object type that holds index, part number, cage number, description, units of assembly, usable on code, and SMR code
    Author:
    Bernard Chan, Sonali Loomba
